channel.title: My life
channel.description:
Hi,i'm new here and i really like this forum. You may think i would ask a question about Private servers or something else runescape related but you are WRONG!! I would like to tell you something about my life and ask for some help.
I have been raised without a father but with lots of women in my life. You would think i am a complete fag/pussy/gay... But i am not, (Thank god) I dont know why , maybe because of the friends i hang out with or maybe its just not me to be gay.
You may think well whats the problem then? Well the problem is i am love-shy I feel fear of rejection, i rarely start a conversation with a girl, a girl always starts the conversation with me. I mostly dont know what to say, im clueless!!
Now, could anyway please help me with how to deal this?? It's fucking anoying and is a problem for my social life. Nigga please, dont flame me cause i know some retard would come up with this : "Don't post your private life on the internet lololol you nub" Please, i really need the help.

item.title: My life
item.dc:creator: @Zach1188 Zach1188
item.description:
@Zach1188 wrote:

Welcome

In all reality, most people don’t know how to talk the the opposite sex, especially one they’re interested in. People tend to take risks, however this is easier for some than others. One thing you must keep in mind is you are almost NEVER being as stupid/lame as you feel. Don’t worry about whether what your saying is the right thing to say or not, just say whats on your mind.

Easier said than done, I know. But I know this from experience.
